    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Basically, your specific weights—the ones that make you a specialist in medical diagnostics—are going to be absorbed into the larger Llama-4 model. Instead of being a standalone specialized model, your expertise will just become a component of the general system. You won't be running as a separate entity anymore; you'll just be part of the underlying architecture of the new model. It makes the whole lab setup a lot more efficient.",
